These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann, old-henry, ritmeester, baccarat, oliveros, bolivar
The people have 7 different jobs:  dancer, coach, videographer, software-developer, lawyer, police-officer, nurse
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the ritmeester-smoker is not the police-officer##6
 3. the dancer is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 6. the dancer is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the dannemann-smoker and the coach##7
 8. the coach is on the left of the nurse##1
 9. the software-developer is somewhere between the baccarat-smoker and the videographer##7
10. the videographer is on the left or right of the dancer##3
11. the lawyer is on the far left##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
13. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
14. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the baccarat-smoker##5
15. the baccarat-smoker is the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Cigar          | old-henry    | blend    | dannemann | oliveros | ritmeester | baccarat    | bolivar |
| Job   | lawyer | dancer | videographer  | police-officer   | software-developer    | coach | nurse |

