.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-2::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, lemonade, mirinda, water, cola, 7up
The people have 7 different jobs:  videographer, doctor, freelancer, social-worker, accountant, firefighter, paramedic
 1. the firefighter is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking tea##7
 2. the paramedic is the person drinking mirinda##1
 3. the accountant is on the right of the paramedic##1
 4. the paramedic is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the social-worker and the doctor##7
 6. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the freelancer##7
 7. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking tea##7
 8. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 9. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
10. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
11. the firefighter is not the person drinking 7up##6
12. the doctor is on the right of the firefighter##1
13. the accountant is between the social-worker and the person drinking mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |       5       |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage    | 7up  | lemonade | cola | mirinda | coffee     | water | tea  |
| Job   | freelancer | firefighter | doctor  | paramedic  | accountant | social-worker      | videographer |

