 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the boat##7
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
11. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
13. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in september##7
14. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
15. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
16. the person who's birthday is in september is not the person driving the roller##6
17. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
18. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
19. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5

