.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-16::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: water, tea, soy-milk, milk, lemonade, almond-milk, fanta
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, turkish, pakistani, chinese, indian, italian, spanish
 1. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the indian and the chinese##7
 2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 3. the spanish is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking lemonade##2
 4. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
 5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the japanese is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
 8. the italian is the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
10. the spanish is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
12. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
13. the japanese is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the chinese##7
14. the person drinking lemonade is the turkish##1
15. the spanish is the person drinking water##1
16. the spanish is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
17. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
18. the japanese is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |     7     |
| Beverage       | almond-milk | water | lemonade | fanta | milk     | tea | soy-milk  |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | spanish   | turkish   | indian | italian | japanese    | chinese |

