.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-17::.
There are 7 different nationalities: american, pakistani, thai, spanish, turkish, indonesian, french
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: action, crime, epic, animation, superhero, family, time-travel
 1. the french is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
 2. the spanish is on the left of the indonesian##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching epic movies and the person watching time-travel movies##7
 4. the american is not the person watching epic movies##6
 5. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
 6. the american is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 7. the american is somewhere to the right of the french##5
 8. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the american is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching action movies is not the pakistani##6
11. the person watching epic movies is the spanish##1
12. the thai is on the far left##1
13. the french is not the person watching time-travel movies##6
14. the person watching crime movies is the french##1
15. the spanish is in an even position##4
16. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
17. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the french and the person watching epic movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |       2        |      3      |        4        |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | thai  | pakistani     | french | turkish         | american | spanish | indonesian |
| Movie-Genre     | animation | time-travel | crime   | family | superhero    | epic      | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-18::.
7 different games are played: scrabble, poker, monopoly, chess, snooker, whist, backgammon
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, weightlifting, soccer, basketball, cricket, rugby, ice-hockey
 1. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##5
 2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person playing backgammon##5
 3. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing snooker is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
 6. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 7. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the person playing scrabble##6
12. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
13. the person who's sport is handball is not the person playing monopoly##6
14. the person who's sport is cricket is the person playing monopoly##1
15. the person who's sport is rugby is not the person playing scrabble##6
16. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the person playing snooker##5
17. the person playing scrabble is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is basketball##7
18. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
19. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person playing chess and the person who's sport is cricket##2
20. the person playing chess is not the person who's sport is rugby##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7    |
| Game         | monopoly  | whist | chess   | poker | snooker    | scrabble | backgammon |
| Sport   | cricket | soccer  | weightlifting | handball  | rugby | ice-hockey    | basketball |

