.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-19::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, milk, juice, cola, tea, lemonade
7 different games are played: whist, snooker, chess, backgammon, mah-jongg, poker, bridge
 1. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
 3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 4. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person playing whist and the person drinking lemonade##7
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person playing poker##5
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
10. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
12. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
13. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
14. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing poker##1
15. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
16. the person playing backgammon is not the person drinking juice##6
17. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
18. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person playing poker##7
19. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3     |      4       |     5     |     6     |     7      |
| Beverage   | lemonade | tea   | cola | milk | mirinda | iced-tea | juice |
| Game   | chess      | backgammon | whist | mah-jongg    | bridge      | poker  | snooker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-20::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, sunflower, dahlia, tulip, marigold, daisy
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: horror, romance, action, epic, time-travel, disaster, sports
 1. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
 2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 3. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person watching epic movies##7
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growssunflower##5
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
 9. the person watching horror movies is the person who growstulip##1
10. the person watching epic movies is the person who growsdahlia##1
11. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
12. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbellflower##5
13. the person who growsmarigold is on the far left##1
14. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who growsdaisy##1
15. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
16. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
17. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
18. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
19. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |  3   |    4     |    5    |      6       |    7    |
| Flower       | marigold | dahlia | sunflower | iris | tulip | daisy | bellflower |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | epic | action  | romance      | horror    | time-travel         | disaster    |

 